  <div class="content" style="padding-top:16px">
    <div class="content-row col-2">
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-header">Competitive Density Score</div>
        <div class="card-body">
          <p style="font-size:12px;color:var(--slate);line-height:1.6;margin-bottom:14px">Opportunities per 100K population in a CBSA, normalized 0–100.<br><strong style="color:var(--navy)">High</strong> = crowded market &nbsp;·&nbsp; <strong style="color:var(--navy)">Low</strong> = underpenetrated opportunity<br><span style="font-size:11px">Key inputs: opportunity count, population size, chain %, service overlap</span></p>
          <div class="donut-wrap">
            <div class="donut"></div>
